										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.atfx.com.bz/zh-hant/live-chart/eur-usd" target="_blank" rel="noopener">歐元兌美元</a>匯率以1.0350開局，交易者熱議歐元與美元達到平價的可能性。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-44378" src="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/EURUSD-–-Daily-Chart.png" alt="EURUSD – Daily Chart" width="1119" height="592" srcset="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/EURUSD-–-Daily-Chart.png 1119w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/EURUSD-–-Daily-Chart-300x159.png 300w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/EURUSD-–-Daily-Chart-1024x542.png 1024w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/EURUSD-–-Daily-Chart-768x406.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1119px) 100vw, 1119px" /></p>
